    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. Discretization error achieved Gradation 3, exceeding the Gradation 2 requirement. Output comparison MAPE of 8.3% is within the defined acceptance band. The UQ ensemble campaign confirmed that model predictions bracket experimental scatter at the 90th-percentile level. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied at all 5 COU operating points. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
